.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, sunflower, zinnia
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the person who growszinnia is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Flower   | iris    | sunflower | zinnia | bellflower        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

