.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, whist, go
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary, mystery
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, pakistani, spanish
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person playing snooker##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing go##1
6. the person playing monopoly is the pakistani##1
7. the spanish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Game         | go   | whist   | monopoly | snooker |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure | disaster   | mystery |
| Nationality   | spanish     | canadian  | pakistani  | german  |

