4. the person eating papaya is on the right of the chef##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
6. the person eating onion is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
