4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, rat, turtle
1. the engineer is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the scientist##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the owner of the rat##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the security-guard is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | scientist  | dressmaker | security-guard |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| Pet         | mouse | rat    | ferret   | turtle         |

 